{
  "id": 135027,
  "name": "Remove The Shadow Gradient on YouTube Video Player",
  "description": "Removes the shadow gradient behind the YouTube video player bar and gradient above. Helps a little bit with reading and seeing stuff normally hidden by this bar. :P I miss the old player that didn't cover videos :'/\r\nI've made the option to set the opacity between 0% and 100% to vary how visible the gradients are. hope you enjoy~ ^_^\r\nI'll try find out if I can give the option to color them, I'm still learning. let me know in the comments if you want this feature, cheers. :D\r\n\r\n-If you want the Player bar to be moved below the video, try my other style for it: style 137651",
